Joffe%2C+Lawrence&amp;rft.aulast=Joffe&amp;rft.date=26+June+2007&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2007%2Fjun%2F26%2Fguardianobituaries.israel&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Guardian&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-haaretz2-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-haaretz2_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-haaretz2_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-haaretz2_4-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"citation news\">Karpel, Dalia (19 October 2006). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.haaretz.com/a-life-less-ordinary-1.202850\">\"A life less ordinary\"</a>. <i>Haaretz</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">9 September</span> 2011</span>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABaruch+Kimmerling&amp;rft.atitle=A+life+less+ordinary&amp;rft.aufirst=Dalia&amp;rft.au=Karpel%2C+Dalia&amp;rft.aulast=Karpel&amp;rft.date=19+October+2006&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fa-life-less-ordinary-1.202850&amp;rft.jtitle=Haaretz&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"citation news\">Lynfield, Ben (12 May 2005). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csmonitor.com/2005/0512/p06s01-wome.html\">\"British boycott riles Israeli academics\"</a>. <i>The Christian Science Monitor</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">10 September</span> 2011</span>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=i